Verify the systemwide shared library directories "/lib", "/lib64", "/usr/lib", and "/usr/lib64" are owned by root with the following command: 

$ sudo find /lib /lib64 /usr/lib /usr/lib64 ! -user root -type d -exec stat -c "%n %U" '{}' \; 

If any systemwide library directory is returned, this is a finding.
